master.commit_message:
Add cllayerinfo tool (#27)

* Move layer API definition to ocl_icd_loader.h

* Add cllayerinfo utility.

* Add name info to our dummy layer.

* Add test for cllayerinfo.

* Remove CL_API_ENTRY decorator from function type definitions.

Update pkg-config file to reflect new OpenCL-Headers pkgconfig support. (#26)

* Update pkg-config file to reflect new OpenCL-Headers pkgconfig support.

* Remove Cflags from OpenCL.pc file as Cflags will come from the OpenCL-Headers.pc
Rely on branch predictor to avoid overhead of layer dispatch. (#30)
Update Khronos headers to latest release. (#29)
Add CL_NO_NON_ICD_DISPATCH_EXTENSION_PROTOTYPES to avoid non exported function definitions. (#28)

Added support for system layers. (#23)

* Added support for system layers.

* Remove code duplication in directory scan code.

* Put system layer initialization in its own subroutine.
